description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen at the RCH for an enthusiastic, motivated, and hardworking individual to join the team. You will be responsible for receipting and checking of all deliveries within the Catering Department at Royal Cornwall NHS Trust. Ensuring all stock is stored and rotated appropriately, following set procedures and specifications. This position requires flexibility to accommodate the needs of the service, good communication skills and a positive and professional attitude.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a full time post working 37.5 hours per week.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Helen Tyler, Head of Catering , helen.tyler3@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
